reviewText: Case was broken. Otherwise I like it.
It's Garth Brooks!! - Need I say more??!!
I love Garth Brooks and wish he would start making new music.  Loved his concert at the Wynn in Las Vegas too.  He is still relavant.

Anonymous and I Don't Have To Wonder are not on the Garth Brooks Ultimate Garth Brooks 3 Disc Set
which is a shame because they are awesome. Neither have his music video The River on it which is a bummer too.
I like Garth Brooks and I am a big fan of his,yet it is hard for fans like myself not finding all of his music videos
because I know that he did more than he is putting these music video collection,yet still this DVD is worth the purchase.
You get like 10 music videos which are to me some of his best music videos period.

The Ultimate Garth Brooks DVD does not have interviews like this DVD which I really do not understand
even though I try to understand things from his point of view.
This is not much more than some brief 1 minute interviews and a few music videos.  its worth $5 if you're a Garth fan, but otherwise save your money.

WOW!!!  I can't believe how quick this came!  I actually added it to my order for someone I work with - and go figure, out of the 7 items, hers came first!  Thanks also for the note along with it!  Hope next time I can deal with you more!!!!  Have a great holiday and thanks again!!!!

This item is a definite must have for Garth Brooks fans. My favorite parts were all the interviews in the bonus features. The interviews on this video really give you an inside look at Garth's retired life. :) This is a definite must have for the big Garth fanatics like me. :)
